// DESIGN SPEC — generated by Designer agent
// Coder: implement TODO items, do not change component structure or accessibility attributes
//
// StoryTimelinePanel
// ──────────────────
// Center-area content for the project workspace "时间线" (timeline) tab. Renders
// the current episode's generation workflow DAG (top) and its run history
// timeline (bottom). Read-only MVP — surfaces the already-computed
// `currentStoryWorkflowNodes` / `currentStoryRuns` projections from
// ProjectWorkspacePage that are currently calculated but never rendered.
//
// All data is owned by the parent (page); this component is purely
// presentational. Selection is emitted so the page can open the relevant
// node / run detail. Re-run / regenerate affordances are out of scope here.
//
// Layout, top → bottom:
//   1. Workflow DAG — one card per node: tool-kind glyph, label, model,
//      dependency hints (dependsOn count), latest-run status dot. Dependency
//      *edges* are represented textually (count + names) rather than as a
//      drawn graph, which the coder may upgrade later.
//   2. Run history — reverse-chronological timeline: status badge, thumbnail,
//      truncated prompt, model, time. status drives the accent color.
// Each section degrades to a dashed empty placeholder when its data is empty.

<template>
  <section class="story-timeline" aria-label="生成时间线">
    <div class="story-timeline__scroll">
      <!-- ── 1. Workflow DAG ──────────────────────────────────────── -->
      <section class="dag" aria-labelledby="timeline-dag-heading">
        <div class="section-head">
